  "Typically not offered, or charged separately.": "Biasanya tidak ditawarkan, atau dikenakan biaya terpisah.",
  "Included with every courseware engagement.": "Termasuk dalam setiap penugasan courseware.",
  "Submission record and experience": "Rekam jejak dan pengalaman pengajuan",
  "Often a single hand, with limited submission experience.": "Sering kali hanya satu orang, dengan pengalaman pengajuan terbatas.",
  "Close to one hundred courseware submissions, made collectively as a team.": "Hampir seratus pengajuan courseware, dilakukan bersama sebagai tim.",
  "Revenue and marketing": "Pendapatan dan pemasaran",
  "Referred to a separate vendor.": "Dirujuk ke vendor terpisah.",
  "Handled by the practice.": "Ditangani oleh practice.",
  "Practice · V": "Practice · V",
  "The shape of correspondence, monochrome study, the solidity of a working practice.": "Bentuk korespondensi, studi monokrom, kekokohan sebuah practice yang bekerja.",
  "Tell us a little about your sector and the courses you train. We will be in touch about adding you to the community.": "Ceritakan sedikit tentang sektor Anda dan kursus yang Anda latih. Kami akan menghubungi Anda mengenai penambahan Anda ke komunitas.",
  "Tell us about your domain and where you have practised. We will write back about engagements we are working on that may fit your standing.": "Ceritakan kepada kami tentang domain Anda dan di mana Anda pernah berpraktik. Kami akan membalas tentang penugasan yang sedang kami kerjakan yang mungkin cocok dengan kedudukan Anda.",
  "Received": "Diterima",
  "Your note has reached the practice, and is in good hands. You will hear from us at hello@2birds.asia within two working days.": "Catatan Anda telah sampai ke practice, dan berada di tangan yang tepat. Anda akan mendengar dari kami di hello@2birds.asia dalam dua hari kerja.",
  "Your name": "Nama Anda",
