  "Founder · Curriculum Developer In House Legal Counsel": "Pendiri · Pengembang Kurikulum Penasihat Hukum Internal",
  "Bachelor of Laws (Hons) (UK) SDip (HRM), MSHRI DACE, ACLP, ACTA, IAL-SAE TAEPP Level 3 Senior Professional AE HRD Corp Accredited Trainer (Msia) Verify TAEPP ↗": "Sarjana Hukum (Hons) (UK) SDip (HRM), MSHRI DACE, ACLP, ACTA, IAL-SAE TAEPP Level 3 Senior Professional AE Pelatih Terakreditasi HRD Corp (Msia) Verifikasi TAEPP ↗",
  "keith.ho@2birds.asia": "keith.ho@2birds.asia",
  "Keith Ho is a training and education professional with more than a decade in the Training and Adult Education sector. He serves as General Manager of 1ST Aid and Healthcare Pte. Ltd. and runs 2birds, an independent advisory and course development practice.": "Keith Ho adalah seorang profesional pelatihan dan pendidikan dengan lebih dari satu dekade di sektor Pelatihan dan Pendidikan Dewasa. Ia menjabat sebagai General Manager 1ST Aid and Healthcare Pte. Ltd. dan menjalankan 2birds, sebuah practice penasihat dan pengembangan kursus independen.",
  "He holds a Bachelor of Laws (Hons) from Birmingham City University, an Allied Certificate in Legal Skills from Temasek Polytechnic, a Specialist Diploma in Human Resource Management from Nanyang Polytechnic, a Diploma in Adult and Continuing Education (DACE) and an Advanced Certificate in Training and Assessment (ACTA) from the Institute for Adult Learning. He is a recognised IAL Specialist Adult Educator, a member of the Singapore Human Resources Institute (MSHRI) and a HRD Corp certified trainer in Malaysia.": "Ia memegang gelar Sarjana Hukum (Hons) dari Birmingham City University, Allied Certificate in Legal Skills dari Temasek Polytechnic, Specialist Diploma in Human Resource Management dari Nanyang Polytechnic, Diploma in Adult and Continuing Education (DACE) dan Advanced Certificate in Training and Assessment (ACTA) dari Institute for Adult Learning. Ia adalah IAL Specialist Adult Educator yang diakui, anggota Singapore Human Resources Institute (MSHRI), dan pelatih bersertifikat HRD Corp di Malaysia.",
  "His career has spanned the Singapore Productivity Centre, the Institute of Singapore Chartered Accountants and Adept Academy. At SGPC, he developed courses including the Fair Tenancy Industry Committee programme, which The Business Times featured in 2022 for promoting the Fair Tenancy Code of Conduct between landlords and tenants. At Adept Academy, he contributed to curriculum development and training innovation and achieved a Grade 1 outcome under SSG's Training Provider Quality Assurance framework. In 2025, SSG invited him as a speaker to share best practices with the training provider community.": "Kariernya membentang dari Singapore Productivity Centre, Institute of Singapore Chartered Accountants, hingga Adept Academy. Di SGPC, ia mengembangkan berbagai kursus termasuk program Fair Tenancy Industry Committee, yang ditampilkan The Business Times pada 2022 karena mempromosikan Fair Tenancy Code of Conduct antara pemilik dan penyewa. Di Adept Academy, ia berkontribusi pada pengembangan kurikulum dan inovasi pelatihan serta meraih hasil Grade 1 di bawah kerangka Training Provider Quality Assurance milik SSG. Pada 2025, SSG mengundangnya sebagai pembicara untuk berbagi praktik terbaik dengan komunitas penyedia pelatihan.",
  "He works within SSG frameworks including WSQ and CASL, and has facilitated training delivery and courseware development for the Singapore Furniture Industries Council Institute, Xprienz, Carrie Academy International, Focus Learning Centre, QD Academy, Addison Institute and HY M&E Consultancy, covering artificial intelligence, healthcare, human resources, legal, leadership, food safety, built environment, data science, supply chain and digital analytics.": "Ia bekerja dalam kerangka SSG termasuk WSQ dan CASL, dan telah memfasilitasi penyampaian pelatihan serta pengembangan courseware untuk Singapore Furniture Industries Council Institute, Xprienz, Carrie Academy International, Focus Learning Centre, QD Academy, Addison Institute, dan HY M&E Consultancy, mencakup kecerdasan buatan, layanan kesehatan, sumber daya manusia, hukum, kepemimpinan, keamanan pangan, lingkungan terbangun, ilmu data, rantai pasok, dan analitik digital.",
  "Correspondence with Keith is welcome by email at keith.ho@2birds.asia.": "Korespondensi dengan Keith disambut melalui email di keith.ho@2birds.asia.",
